(ns farsund.init
  (:require
    [day8.re-frame.async-flow-fx]
    [day8.re-frame.http-fx]
    [taoensso.timbre :as timbre]
    [re-frame.core :as rf]
    [re-frame.router :as router]
    [re-frame.registrar :refer [get-handler clear-handlers register-handler]]
    [re-frame.loggers :refer [console]]

    [farsund.utils.fx]
    [farsund.utils.events]

    [farsund.db.core]
    [farsund.db.fx]
    [farsund.db.events]


    [farsund.ws.fx]
    [farsund.ws.events]
    [farsund.ws.subs]

    [farsund.window.db]
    [farsund.window.fx]
    [farsund.window.events]
    [farsund.window.subs]

    [farsund.process.db]
    [farsund.process.events]
    [farsund.process.subs]

    [farsund.error.db]
    [farsund.error.events]
    [farsund.error.subs]

    [farsund.theme.db]
    [farsund.theme.events]
    [farsund.theme.subs]

    [farsund.ui.db]
    [farsund.ui.events]
    [farsund.ui.subs]

    [farsund.data.db]
    [farsund.data.events]
    [farsund.data.subs]

    [farsund.login.db]
    [farsund.login.events]
    [farsund.data.subs]

    ))

(comment
  farsund.data.db/state
  )
(rf/reg-event-fx
  :farsund/boot
  (fn [_ _]
    {:db (merge farsund.db.core/default-db
                farsund.window.db/state
                farsund.process.db/state
                farsund.error.db/state
                farsund.theme.db/state
                farsund.ui.db/state
                farsund.data.db/state
                farsund.login.db/state


                (farsund.db.core/load-local-storage))
     :async-flow
         {:first-dispatch [:window/run-resize-listener!]
          :rules          [{:when     :seen? :events :window/run-resize-listener!
                            :dispatch [:ws/start]}
                           {:when     :seen? :events :window/run-resize-listener!
                            :dispatch [:window/run-scroll-listener!]}
                           {:when       :seen? :events :chsk/handshake
                            :dispatch-n [[:data/get-market-report]
                                         [:data/get-product-stock]
                                         [:data/get-cg-data]
                                         [:data/get-market-order]
                                         ]}
                           ]}}))
